{"tid":1799524,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黑警6至11月工作相關及膳食津貼達1億3500萬元","createTime":"2019-12-27T04:38:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-27T04:56:20.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"317b59b7f81ce16eeffaf7853fe739a4805d2a19","tid":1799524,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T04:38:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1499775-20191227.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1499775-20191227.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=TEMpI0ru4fZij%2BnpPgfFHQsTF5hDypdTwPi8eTnvKzQ%3D&h=199b81f6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1499775-20191227.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=a69f6fbf\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1499775-20191227.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n警務處由6月至11月的工作相關津貼及本地膳食津貼總開支，分別為8500萬及5000萬元。<br />\n<br />\n保安局及公務員事務局回應議員朱凱廸要求，向立法會財委會交代有關金額。<br />\n<br />\n較早前，保安局表示，過去半年，警務處平均每月有約11000人，領取紀律部隊逾時工作津貼，涉及的總開支是9億5千萬元。"},{"pid":"b6b3f61ee5623e1b770d71e8c30466d545bc182d","tid":1799524,"uid":113155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T04:44:31.000Z","msg":"食咩食3500萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cf6bab00c54453a061263c89580877a1ec6a1ea","tid":1799524,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b6b3f61ee5623e1b770d71e8c30466d545bc182d","tid":1799524,"uid":113155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T04:44:31.000Z","msg":"食咩食3500萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T04:45:02.000Z","msg":"係5千萬"},{"pid":"4d8d7c7c932354be9467a1a09d96b1cdf0a640fe","tid":1799524,"uid":113155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2cf6bab00c54453a061263c89580877a1ec6a1ea","tid":1799524,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc